{
  "stem": "22944.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I do know my late brother and father were beaten up quite a lot, 'cause my father was taken-- brought back one day-- been attacked by some more young people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were hiding in the bushes, and when they passed through, they knew he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And probably he kept his Star of David on, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so they knew that something serious is happening now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they have to make a decision.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they send my brother away to Hungary with my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my father lived in fear, like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We started really realizing, but my mother-- sister Ella, had quite a good connection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And strange enough, we had a connection with somebody who was belonged to a Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But he was still a friend of our family, and he really warned us quite often.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I would have liked to mention it, but I can't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he would occasionally, via my aunt, that things-- what to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he may have, as far as-- I don't know really.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He may have even warned my auntie that my brother should go away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But he helped us-- this man, who was so-called, or he was in a party, Hlinka Party, what was a-- a movement that followed the Hitler ideology.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I think that Tiso-- you probably must have heard about Tiso.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was a priest who was arousing quite a bit the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was a real anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --he warned, occasionally, our family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And when, all of a sudden, they start the Jews be sent away to labor camp, we really did not know what to do.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
